mpv configs
=====

### Note, vaapi (Intel) support may not work on your machine or you use Nvidia, then adjust for vdpau, otherwise use the defaults or change to xv

==== config_ivan_20140227:

basic and well commented mpv config with vaapi support enabled using opengl, loads all subs contained in one directory

==== input.conf_ivan_20140227:

change aspect ratio with the keys F1 - F5
